{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"StorageEvent","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent\"><code>StorageEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent/initStorageEvent\"><code>initStorageEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Web Storage API 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage\"><code>Window.localStorage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>Window.sessionStorage</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>当前页面使用的 storage 被其他页面修改时会触发 StorageEvent 事件。</p>\n<p>[译者：事件在同一个域下的不同页面之间触发，即在 A 页面注册了 storge 的监听处理，只有在跟 A 同域名下的 B 页面操作 storage 对象，A 页面才会被触发 storage 事件]</p><svg viewBox=\"-1 -1 650 42\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin meet\">\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\">\n    <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"75\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"37.5\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      Event\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"75\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"105\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" \"=\"\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"75,14 85,9 85,19 75,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent\" aria-current=\"page\">\n    <rect x=\"105\" y=\"0\" width=\"96\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#F4F7F8\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"153\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      StorageEvent\n    </text>\n  </a></svg>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 尽管这个事件已经早在 <span title=\"(Firefox 4 / Thunderbird 3.3 / SeaMonkey 2.1)\">Gecko&nbsp;2.0</span>时就已存在，但是并不符合规范。老的事件模型直到 <code>nsIDOMStorageEventObsolete</code> 确定才被表现出来。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法描述","title":"方法描述","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">void initStorageEvent(\n  in DOMString typeArg,\n  in boolean canBubbleArg,\n  in boolean cancelableArg,\n  in DOMString keyArg,\n  in DOMString oldValueArg,\n  in DOMString newValueArg,\n  in DOMString urlArg,\n  in nsIDOMStorage storageAreaArg\n);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>属性名</th>\n      <th>类型</th>\n      <th>描述</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>key</code></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/DOMString\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n      <td>该属性代表被修改的键值。当被 clear() 方法清除之后该属性值为 null。<strong>（只读）</strong></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>newValue</code></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/DOMString\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n      <td>该属性代表修改后的新值。当被 clear() 方法清理后或者该键值对被移除，<code>newValue</code> 的值为 <code>null</code> 。<strong>（只读）</strong></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>oldValue</code></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/DOMString\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n      <td>该属性代表修改前的原值。在设置新键值对时由于没有原始值，该属性值为 <code>null</code>。<strong>（只读）</strong></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>storageArea</code></td>\n      <td><code>nsIDOMStorage</code></td>\n      <td>被操作的 storage 对象。<strong>（只读）</strong></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>url</code></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/DOMString\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n      <td>key 发生改变的对象所在文档的 URL 地址。<strong>（只读）</strong></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"initstorageevent","title":"initStorageEvent()","isH3":true,"content":"<p>类似 DOM 中的初始化事件，即初始化新创建的 Storage 对象的属性。</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">void initStorageEvent(\n  in DOMString typeArg,\n  in boolean canBubbleArg,\n  in boolean cancelableArg,\n  in DOMString keyArg,\n  in DOMString oldValueArg,\n  in DOMString newValueArg,\n  in DOMString urlArg,\n  in nsIDOMStorage storageAreaArg\n);\n</pre>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"sect2\">\n    <p>参数：</p>\n    <p><code>typeArg</code></p>\n  </dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>事件名</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"canbubblearg\"><code>canBubbleArg</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>布尔值，代表是否可以通过 dom 冒泡</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cancelablearg\"><code>cancelableArg</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>布尔值，代表是否可以注销事件</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"keyarg\"><code>keyArg</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>事件结果时被改变的值对应的属性名称</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"oldvaluearg\"><code>oldValueArg</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>旧值</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"newvaluearg\"><code>newValueArg</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>新值</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"urlarg\"><code>urlArg</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>事件初始化时页面的 url</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"storageareaarg\"><code>storageAreaArg</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>发生在哪个 storage 对象上</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webstorage.html#the-storageevent-interface","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.StorageEvent"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参阅","title":"参阅","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://dev.w3.org/html5/webstorage/#the-storage-event\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Specification</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"方法描述","id":"方法描述"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"参阅","id":"参阅"}],"summary":"当前页面使用的 storage 被其他页面修改时会触发 StorageEvent 事件。","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"StorageEvent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"StorageEvent","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"StorageEvent","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/storageevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/storageevent/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent","title":"StorageEvent"}],"pageTitle":"StorageEvent - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}